---




  <!--OVERVIEW -->

  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center w-full " id="overview">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-start w-full text-center text-black px-6">
              <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="text-4xl font-medium font-['Playfair_Display'] w-full text-center">BrightWaste Sustainable Web App</h1>
              <p
              class="relative self-stretch mt-2 [font-family:'Playfair_Display-Bold',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-2xl text-center tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
            >
              <span class="font-bold">ðŸ¥³ </span>
              <span class="font-['Playfair_Display'] font-medium"
              >Courier Hacks Winner
              </span>
              <span class="font-bold">ðŸ¥³ </span>
            </p>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base  w-full text-center max-w-[45rem] m-auto">
                A Sustainable Marketplace Website that can give people options either
                to 
                  <em class="font-semibold">sell the used items directly to the shop</em> or <em>upcycle and sell it for a better price</em>.
              </p>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-block w-full h-6"></div>
          <Image src={brightwaste} alt="Shopping Cart" class="w-full m-auto max-w-[64rem]" />
      </div>
  </div>




  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-8 lg:gap-0 my-8 lg:max-w-[45rem] mx-auto w-full px-6">

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center w-full">
        <img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/fbcfdd4c80eb7c7c5c10f2580f396cdd7782510a9fe922c1affb8999734678bd?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=36a6ec44b2c9485d99179a8191a89170" alt="Team icon" class="object-contain w-8 aspect-square" />
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="mt-2 text-xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-medium">TEAM</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-center max-w-[15rem]">
          2 developers, and myself as a UX Designer and UX Writer
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center  w-full ">
        <img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/d389f29f09756e8e8c2dc739c56961ec83c6a1afc90fbed2aace39913a324d40?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=36a6ec44b2c9485d99179a8191a89170" alt="Duration icon" class="object-contain w-8 aspect-square" />
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="mt-2 text-xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-medium">DURATION</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm"> Oct 2022 - Mar 2023</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center  w-full ">
        <img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/7db918896ed84cff0b1e96aa204ecc21a2cfce91d404d42a38ed02718e46a06b?placeholderIfAbsent=true&apiKey=36a6ec44b2c9485d99179a8191a89170" alt="Tools icon" class="object-contain w-8 aspect-square" />
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;" class="mt-2 text-xl font-['Playfair_Display'] font-medium">TOOLS</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Figma, Github,
          Visual Studio Code</p>
    </div>
</div>




  <div class="w-full lg:max-w-[45rem] mx-auto px-6 mt-8">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4 relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto]"
    >
      <p
        class="relative self-stretch mt-[-1.00px] font-['Playfair_Display'] font-normal text-transparent text-lg tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
      >
        <span class="font-bold text-[#5a3dff]">
          OVERVIEW
          <br />
        </span>
        <span
          class="font-['Playfair_Display'] font-semibold text-[#020202] text-xl"
        >
          Analyze the goal of BrightWaste
        </span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <p
          class="relative self-stretch [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
        >
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
          >
            Our main goal was to encourage people to live sustainably and earn
            more money at the same time. The idea of recycling has been a trend
            since years ago. The question is, does it work?
            <br />
          </span>
        </p>
        <p
          class="relative self-stretch [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
        >
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
          >
            <br />
          </span>
        </p>
        <p
          class="relative self-stretch [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
        >
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
          >
            Based on the research,
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex items-start my-4 justify-center gap-[140px] relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto] "
    >
      <div
        class="flex px-[10%] items-start gap-2.5 py-4 relative  flex-1 grow bg-[#DAD4FE] rounded-[15px]"
      >
        <svg
          class="w-6 md:w-[70px]"
          viewBox="0 0 72 70"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M43.373 39.355C43.373 37.32 42.6934 35.56 41.3002 34.13C39.1934 31.985 35.0817 31.71 32.703 32.15C31.7176 27.6125 36.4749 21.8375 42.6254 19.3625L37.9021 14C28.6253 17.575 19.4845 25.77 21.0476 36.1375C22.0331 42.6825 26.7224 47 33.3487 47C36.237 47 38.6497 46.3125 40.5526 44.9375C42.4555 43.5625 43.373 41.6925 43.373 39.355ZM70.7275 39.355C70.7275 37.32 70.0479 35.56 68.6547 34.13C66.5139 31.985 62.4362 31.71 60.0575 32.15C59.0721 27.6125 63.8294 21.8375 69.9799 19.3625L65.2566 14C55.9799 17.575 46.873 25.77 48.4361 36.1375C49.4216 42.6825 54.0769 47 60.7032 47C63.5915 47 66.0042 46.3125 67.9071 44.9375C69.81 43.5625 70.7275 41.6925 70.7275 39.355Z"
            fill="#5585FF"></path>
        </svg>

        <p
          class="relative flex-1 mt-[-1.00px] [font-family:'Playfair_Display'] font-normal text-[#020202] text-xl tracking-[0] leading-[40.3px]"
        >
          <span
            class="font-['Playfair_Display'] font-medium italic"
          >
            About 110 million glass bottles are thrown away and only one-third
            get recycled.{' '}
          </span>
          <span class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica]"
          >-- weforum.org</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p
      class="relative self-stretch [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
    >
      It could be easier to sell the used item for a lower price, but instead of
      doing so,
    </p>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4 relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto]"
    >
      <div
        class="relative self-stretch mt-4 font-['Playfair_Display'] font-semibold text-[#020202] text-xl tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
