      >
        get our creativity going and turn it into something more meaningful and
        can have more value to it?&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <br />
        <br />
        It doesn&#39;t only impact the earth; also, we can contribute to the economy
        cycle.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto]"
    >
      <div
        class="relative self-stretch mt-[-1.00px] [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
      >
        Thatâ€™s why we provided...
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex items-start justify-center gap-[140px] relative self-stretch w-full flex-[0_0_auto]"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2.5 my-4 p-4 relative flex-1 grow bg-[#aae5fe] rounded-[15px]"
      >
        <div
          class="relative w-fit mt-[-1.00px] font-['Playfair_Display'] font-bold text-[#020202] text-2xl tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
        >
          Brightwaste
        </div>
        <p
          class="relative self-stretch [font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0] leading-[normal]"
        >
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
          >
            ...which helps people to get{' '}
          </span>
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-SemiBoldItalic',Helvetica] font-semibold italic"
          >
            plenty of ideas on how to recycle
          </span>
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
          >
            {' '}
            their stuff and lets the potential seller get notified{' '}
          </span>
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-SemiBoldItalic',Helvetica] font-semibold italic"
          >
            when they can sell the products for a better price
          </span>
          <span
            class="[font-family:'Open_Sans-Regular',Helvetica] font-normal text-[#020202] text-base lg:text-sm tracking-[0]"
